name: RabbitSwap
description: What is RabbitSwap (RABBIT)? RabbitSwap is a decentralized swap on BSC chain with high APR on farming and lowest fees. RabbitSwap helps you make the most out of your crypto in three ways: Trade, Earn and Win. RABBIT is the delicious token that powers the RabbitSwap ecosystem. Earn RABBIT from Farms and Syrup Pools, win it in the lottery, or buy it on the exchange, then explore its use cases: - Stake it in Syrup Pools to earn free tokens - Use it in Yield Farms to earn more RABBIT - Buy Lottery tickets in the RabbitSwap Lottery - Participate in IFO Token Sales - Create your RabbitSwap Profile and mint NFTs - Vote on proposals relating to the RabbitSwap ecosystem
